to die that day.

00:13.143 --> 00:15.102
Greatest four hours
and 22 minutes of my life.

00:15.189 --> 00:15.885
And I was at Woodstock.

00:15.972 --> 00:18.801
Move your feet.

00:18.888 --> 00:20.237
I don't want to;
just sit in the chair.

00:20.324 --> 00:21.760
But it's a bad angle.

00:21.847 --> 00:23.501
My neck will seize
by the fourth touchdown.

00:23.588 --> 00:25.199
[groans] My one day off,

00:25.286 --> 00:27.984
I can't even watch a
20-year-old football game.

00:28.071 --> 00:29.681
Mike, look.

00:29.768 --> 00:31.161
I got published.

00:31.248 --> 00:32.336
