02:08.258 --> 02:09.955
Just last week, I helped
a prince from Nigeria

02:10.042 --> 02:12.001
track down his fortune.

02:14.395 --> 02:16.266
Listen, what do you say
we get all dolled up

02:16.353 --> 02:18.094
and I take you out
to lunch to celebrate?

02:18.181 --> 02:19.530
Oh, what about your day off

02:19.617 --> 02:20.836
and your goal
to not move an inch?

02:20.923 --> 02:24.709
[scoffs]
He already ruined that.

02:24.796 --> 02:27.016
Plus, it's not every day my
wife gets read by millions.

02:27.103 --> 02:29.671
Oh, well, I think
it's more like...

02:29.758 --> 02:31.281
