get near them.

04:31.488 --> 04:33.490
So, how would you like to spend

04:33.577 --> 04:35.405
the rest of our day
of celebration?

04:35.492 --> 04:36.798
And please don't
say martial arts movie,

04:36.885 --> 04:39.453
center row, third aisle,
large popcorn.

04:39.540 --> 04:40.584
