05:07.655 --> 05:09.613
Oh, come on.
Can you just relax, fella?

05:09.700 --> 05:12.268
Can we just go in,
have some fun?

05:12.355 --> 05:13.182
Do something new?

05:13.269 --> 05:14.662
Come on, let's go in.

05:14.749 --> 05:16.011
No, you're gonna get us
in trouble.

05:16.098 --> 05:18.840
With who?The Rolls-Royce people!

05:18.927 --> 05:20.145
