05:20.232 --> 05:21.146
They can't take anything
from us.

05:21.233 --> 05:22.844
We don't have anything.

05:22.931 --> 05:24.628
Molly, do not
go in there.

05:24.715 --> 05:25.847
Molly!

05:25.934 --> 05:27.196
I'm not going in there.

05:27.283 --> 05:29.546
I'm going home.
I'm walking away.

05:29.633 --> 05:31.548
Bye.

05:31.635 --> 05:33.463
They're not gonna... [groans]

05:33.550 --> 05:35.422
Damn it!

05:36.684 --> 05:38.642
