05:57.269 --> 05:58.619
Do you smell that, huh?

05:58.706 --> 06:02.405
It's like we're inside
a James Bond movie.

06:02.492 --> 06:06.235
Leather and the metal
and the...

06:06.322 --> 06:07.845
turkey meatball?

06:07.932 --> 06:08.846
God, Mike!

06:08.933 --> 06:11.501
I'm sorry. I'm nervous.

06:11.588 --> 06:13.111
Can we go?No. We're looking around.

06:13.198 --> 06:15.636
For all they know,
we can afford one of these cars.

06:15.723 --> 06:17.855
Hey, you could have made a lot
of money on the Internet.

06:17.942 --> 06:19.553
You and I both know there's
no money in the Internet.

06:19.640 --> 06:21.468
That's not important.

06:21.555 --> 06:23.339
We can be anybody we want to be.

06:23.426 --> 06:24.993
Okay, it's all in
how you carry yourself.

06:25.080 --> 06:26.298
Just follow my lead.

06:26.386 --> 06:28.213
Have you done
this before?

06:28.300 --> 06:30.128
Not here.

06:30.215 --> 06:32.304
Hello. [chuckles]

06:32.392 --> 06:34.394
Hello.

06:34.481 --> 06:35.699
Can I help you?[in British accent]:
Oh, well, I hope so.

06:35.786 --> 06:37.788
We're quite interested

06:37.875 --> 06:39.007
