07:41.722 --> 07:43.201
Oh, let's try the back.

07:43.288 --> 07:45.508
[classical music blaring]

07:45.595 --> 07:46.814
Is that too loud?

07:46.901 --> 07:48.119
Excuse me?

07:48.206 --> 07:49.033
[regular accent]:
Okay, we're good.

07:49.120 --> 07:50.078
Isn't this great?

07:50.165 --> 07:51.558
Are you having fun?

07:51.645 --> 07:53.037
Don't talk to me;
I'm trying to focus.

07:53.124 --> 07:53.777
