What is wrong with you?

12:38.453 --> 12:40.107
Just go to the stairs.Fine.

12:40.194 --> 12:42.152
But my way
would've worked, too.

12:44.459 --> 12:46.635
[giggling]:
Oh, my God.

12:46.722 --> 12:48.506
We'll just go down a floor,

12:48.593 --> 12:50.508
hop on the elevator,
and we are gone.

12:50.595 --> 12:52.554
You know, I think,
if I put my mind to it,

12:52.641 --> 12:54.338
I could rob a bank.

12:54.425 --> 12:55.775
Take it easy, Bonnie; this
is as far as Clyde goes.

12:55.862 --> 12:58.299
There's no handle.

12:58.386 --> 13:01.302
I guess you're supposed to put
your room key in the slot.

13:01.389 --> 13:02.259
Which we don't have.

13:02.346 --> 13:03.913
Why would they do that?

13:04.000 --> 13:07.221
To prevent people like us
from doing what we did.

13:07.308 --> 13:10.093
Oh, that's actually smart.

13:10.180 --> 13:11.791
What are you doing?

13:11.878 --> 13:14.097
Trying every card
in my wallet.
[chuckles]

13:14.184 --> 13:16.317
Well, I don't think that
your Orange Julius gift card

13:16.404 --> 13:19.059
is gonna save the day.

13:19.146 --> 13:21.844
It's either this
or walk down 71 flights.

13:21.931 --> 13:24.542
Okay, here, try my CVS card.

13:24.629 --> 13:27.807
That hostage thing doesn't look
so bad now, does it?

13:31.680 --> 13:33.551
[panting]

13:33.638 --> 13:34.291
MOLLY:
Whew.

13:34.378 --> 13:36.206
[chuckles]

13:36.293 --> 13:38.382
Ooh, this...

13:38.469 --> 13:40.210
This is quite a workout.

13:40.297 --> 13:40.820
Don't talk to me.

13:40.907 --> 13:42.822
Why?

13:42.909 --> 13:44.519
Because you're gonna
try to make this seem

13:44.606 --> 13:46.129
like we're having fun,
and we're not having fun.

13:46.216 --> 13:49.524
We're 40 floor from fun
with 30 more to go!

13:49.611 --> 13:51.047
Well, see?

13:51.134 --> 13:52.396
We're already halfway there.

13:52.483 --> 13:54.834
Do not look at
the bright side.

13:54.921 --> 13:57.053
There is no
bright side here!

13:57.140 --> 13:59.316
Oh, quit being such a crybaby.

13:59.403 --> 14:00.883
Don't call me a crybaby.

14:00.970 --> 14:04.365
[fake crying]:
Why? You gonna cry, crybaby?

14:04.452 --> 14:06.671
Stop it. If you hadn't dragged
me through all this crap,

14:06.758 --> 14:08.499
I'd be home, happy,
on my couch right now.

14:08.586 --> 14:11.111
But I was just trying to get you
to do something different.

14:11.198 --> 14:13.548
Get you out of your comfort zone
for half a day.

14:13.635 --> 14:14.375
You know what zone I'm in now?

14:14.462 --> 14:16.333
The chafing zone.

14:16.420 --> 14:20.033
I could cook a steak
between my thighs.

14:20.120 --> 14:21.686
Boy, for somebody
who drove a Rolls-Royce today

14:21.773 --> 14:25.081
and had sex
in a five-star hotel for free,

14:25.168 --> 14:26.735
you sure complain a lot.

14:26.822 --> 14:28.737
You know why you can't admit
this is miserable?

14:28.824 --> 14:30.391
Because you live in denial.

14:30.478 --> 14:32.175
That's why
you're so bad with money.

14:32.262 --> 14:34.003
Are you really gonna
point fingers, Groundhog Day?!

14:34.090 --> 14:36.310
I found you on the couch
this morning

14:36.397 --> 14:37.964
watching a 20-year-old
football game!

14:38.051 --> 14:41.402
I might have missed something!

14:41.489 --> 14:43.534
You know what,
I'll see you at the bottom.

14:43.621 --> 14:45.101
Yeah, you know what,
I'll see youat the bottom,

14:45.188 --> 14:46.450
'cause I'm going first!No, I'm going first.

14:46.537 --> 14:48.104
I got the rail.You move your hand.

14:48.191 --> 14:49.714
I got the rail! I got the rail!Move your hand.

14:49.801 --> 14:51.238
[screaming]

14:51.325 --> 14:53.240
Get moving, or I'll
give you the rail!

14:53.327 --> 14:55.285
Yeah, that's my...
[screams]

15:00.116 --> 15:02.075
[panting]

15:03.990 --> 15:05.948
MOLLY:
Mike?

15:08.733 --> 15:10.735
Mike!

15:13.521 --> 15:14.565
What are you doing?

15:14.652 --> 15:17.003
I was down in single digits.

15:17.090 --> 15:19.614
I'm sorry.

15:19.701 --> 15:20.745
That's it.

15:20.832 --> 15:21.921
I can't take another step.

15:22.008 --> 15:24.749
It's only 12 more floors.
Come on.

15:24.836 --> 15:25.576
I can't.

15:25.663 --> 15:26.490
Just leave me.

15:26.577 --> 15:29.145
Live your life.

15:29.232 --> 15:30.494
No.

15:30.581 --> 15:32.757
We walked into this together.

15:32.844 --> 15:34.020
We're walking out
of this together.

15:34.107 --> 15:37.501
I'm just holding you back.

15:37.588 --> 15:38.546
Okay.

15:38.633 --> 15:40.983
We can rest for a second.

15:41.070 --> 15:42.028
I'm not talking
about the stairs.

15:42.115 --> 15:44.595
I'm talking about in life.

15:44.682 --> 15:47.163
I'm just stopping you
from doing all that weird,

15:47.250 --> 15:49.992
wonderful stuff
that you want to do.

15:50.079 --> 15:52.690
Are you kidding?

15:52.777 --> 15:54.954
Mike, I-I couldn't have
done any of that stuff

15:55.041 --> 15:56.738
if it wasn't for you.

15:56.825 --> 15:59.393
That's not true.
It is.

15:59.480 --> 16:01.090
Mike, you're my rock.

16:01.177 --> 16:03.701
If it wasn't for you,

16:03.788 --> 16:06.400
I-I wouldn't have been
able to quit my job

16:06.487 --> 16:09.011
and become the successful,

16:09.098 --> 16:12.319
unpaid internet content
provider I am today.

16:12.406 --> 16:13.929
[laughs]

16:14.016 --> 16:15.539
[sniffles, sighs]

16:15.626 --> 16:18.542
Okay. Now, get up.

16:18.629 --> 16:20.718
Get up,
you exhausted son of a bitch.

16:22.155 --> 16:23.983
Come on.

16:24.070 --> 16:25.854
[groaning]

16:25.941 --> 16:27.073
[panting]

16:27.160 --> 16:28.074
If we don't get out of here,

16:28.161 --> 16:30.859
I love you, Molly.

16:30.946 --> 16:31.903
Then show me.

16:31.991 --> 16:33.993
Show me with your feet!

16:42.001 --> 16:44.742
[alarm blaring]

16:44.829 --> 16:46.788
We did it! We did it!

16:46.875 --> 16:49.051
Sweet baby Jesus,
we're alive!

16:49.138 --> 16:51.967
We're alive!

16:52.054 --> 16:54.013
[sighs]

16:54.100 --> 16:56.580
[alarm continues]

16:56.667 --> 16:58.626
Act like we belong.

17:00.976 --> 17:03.283
Oh, apples!

17:07.678 --> 17:09.071
Thank you. We...

17:09.158 --> 17:11.073
We had a lovely stay.

17:20.126 --> 17:21.344
[sighs]

17:21.431 --> 17:22.476
Come on.

17:22.563 --> 17:24.173
Let's get you to the couch.

17:24.260 --> 17:25.696
[groans]

17:25.783 --> 17:27.698
Can you bring the couch
closer to me?

17:27.785 --> 17:29.787
Come on, honey,
you can do it.

17:29.874 --> 17:31.528
Come on.

17:31.615 --> 17:32.747
Three steps and a flop.

17:32.834 --> 17:35.967
[laughs, groans]

17:36.055 --> 17:38.057
Oh!

17:38.144 --> 17:39.667
[groaning]

17:39.754 --> 17:42.235
Oh, this is comfortable.

17:42.322 --> 17:44.759
Now I know why you never want
to get off of it.

17:44.846 --> 17:46.195
See?

17:46.282 --> 17:47.675
Welcome to Mike Biggs country.

17:47.762 --> 17:50.330
Kind of nice, huh?

17:50.417 --> 17:52.593
Better than a Rolls.

17:52.680 --> 17:54.073
[sighs]

17:54.160 --> 17:55.987
Thank you, Molly.

17:56.075 --> 17:57.598
For what?

17:57.685 --> 17:59.208
Pushing me.

17:59.295 --> 18:00.731
Oh, hey, is that the stairs?

18:00.818 --> 18:02.385
I told you I tripped.

18:02.472 --> 18:04.300
My feet were numb.

18:04.387 --> 18:04.953
[chuckles] No.

18:05.040 --> 18:06.563
[giggles]

18:06.650 --> 18:08.739
For putting
together this day.

18:08.826 --> 18:11.438
Making me do things that...

18:11.525 --> 18:14.093
I-I never thought I would do.

18:14.180 --> 18:16.443
Well, you better get used to it.

18:16.530 --> 18:18.532
I don't know
where I'm going next,

18:18.619 --> 18:20.751
but I'm taking you with me.

18:20.838 --> 18:24.581
Can we at least wait
until my thighs heal

18:24.668 --> 18:29.195
and my ankles go back
to being smaller than my calves?

18:29.282 --> 18:33.460
Well, we can't go Jet Skiing
until the summer anyway.

18:33.547 --> 18:34.852
[groans]

